text: ==Kings of Saudi Arabia (present)== This is a list of rulers of Saudi Arabia, a kingdom on the Arabian Peninsula. ===Sheikhdom of Diriyah=== * 1446–1727 Sheikhdom of Diriyah ===First Saudi State=== * 1727-1818 Emirate of Diriyah ===Second Saudi State=== * 1823-1891 Emirate of Nejd ===Third Saudi State (1902–present)=== *1902 - 1913: Emirate of Riyadh *1913 - 1921: Emirate of Nejd and Hasa *1921 - 1926: Sultanate of Nejd *1926 - 1932: Kingdom of Hejaz and Nejd *1932–present: Kingdom of Saudi Arabia ==References== *
title: List of rulers of Saudi Arabia
